{"tid":1610743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我好似發現咗啲野(大家入黎討論下）","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:17:03.000Z","uid":311563,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"17dee870d26a273ac7b811f2c2ecf143f31ca1bc","tid":1610743,"uid":311563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:36:16.000Z","msg":"睇咗好多post喺度屌後面一喺冇啦啦走哂但係明明前面咩都冇，一喺就行得太慢。  <strong>但呢啲其實都喺代表我地溝通不足同資訊流傳得唔夠快</strong>既然係咁，我就要諗下方法去解決<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我地可以用<ins>樂器</ins>去傳遞訊息，例如  可能要人慢慢後退，就用呢樣<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFakcG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFakcG3.jpg&h=27c113a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能喺一下一下咁撳<br />\n<br />\n而可能要人上前嘅，就用<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDdYJP1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDdYJP1.jpg&h=47bc6fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實用咩<ins>樂器</ins>都冇所謂，但喺要事先有共識咩野代表啲咩，因為我地要嘅其實係類似號角一樣嘅野去傳遞訊息or鼓勵下士氣(甚至乎可能被人包圍又用一種樂器，喺嗰個方向演奏，等大家都知)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好似有啲天馬行空同離地，我唔介意大家恥笑我甚至屌我根本唔理解現實情況，我只喺想睇下有冇方法改善宜家嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>盡情恥笑我啦</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a0f9c2ee18e7d4f48abae07196bad94b4d5050","tid":1610743,"uid":311563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b40e7506880dfea2c0b95556852122862fdd0b","tid":1610743,"uid":311563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:39:42.000Z","msg":"嚟恥笑下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4331ec68e95497be84d96d5a834953096f9a0ecd","tid":1610743,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r